      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "Zermelo-Frankel 集合论公理系统：定义了 Set、Object 类型，以及 ∈、⊆ 等基本关系"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "空集 ∅：通过 emptyset_mem 证明空集无元素"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "单元素集 {a} 和二元集 {a,b}：通过 singleton、pair_eq 定义"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "并集 ∪：union_pair_axiom 证明 x ∈ A ∪ B ↔ x ∈ A ∨ x ∈ B"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "子类型 toSubtype：A.toSubtype 将集合转化为 {x : Object // x ∈ A} 类型"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "交集 ∩ 和差集 \\：通过 specification_axiom 定义"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "替换公理 replace：基于谓词 P 创建新集合"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "自然数 Nat：通过 nat_equiv 与 Mathlib ℕ 建立双射对应"}}]
      }
    },
