        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "Section 3.2: 罗素悖论 (Russell's Paradox)"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "heading_2": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "核心知识点"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "全局规范公理 (Axiom of Universal Specification)：∀P, ∃A, ∀x, x ∈ A ↔ P x"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "罗素悖论证明：定义 P(x) ≡ ∃X, x = X ∧ x ∉ X，导出矛盾"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "正则性公理 (Regularity)：每个非空集合 A 存在最小元 x，使得 x ∩ A = ∅"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "not_mem_self：任何集合 A 都不属于自身"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "heading_2",
      "heading_2": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "难点"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "正则性公理应用：Exercise 3.2.2 需要构造特定集合，利用正则性证明自不相交"}}]
      }
    },
    {
      "object": "block",
      "type": "bulleted_list_item",
      "bulleted_list_item": {
        "rich_text": [{"text": {"content": "choose 策略：使用正则性公理时需要 extract 出 x 的性质"}}]
      }
    },
